('G', 'Tech-Forward & Digital', 'tech-forward', 'Modern tech-integrated gifts that are measurable and shareable.', 'Modern tech-integrated gifts', 'HR/IT', 799, 7999, 'Cpu', 7, 'Tech-Forward & Digital Corporate Gifts | Neon Visuals', 'Smart, tech-integrated corporate gifts with QR, NFC and digital layers that keep gifting alive.', true),
